Insider Activity


Individual




Robert D. Daleo



Mr. Robert D. Daleo is Independent Director at Citrix Systems, Inc., Independent Director at Equifax, Inc., Chairman at Fordham University, and Chairman at New Jersey Community Development Corp. He is on the Board of Directors at Citrix Systems, Inc. and Equifax, Inc.
Mr. Daleo was previously employed as Non-Executive Vice Chairman-Management Board by Thomson Reuters Corp., Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by Thomson Corp., Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by Thomson Reuters Plc, Chief Operating Officer by Thomson Newspapers Ltd., and Chairman-Policy Owners Examining Committee by The Northwestern Mutual Life Insurance Co.
He received his undergraduate degree from Fordham University and an MBA from the City University of New York.



